OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 12 Jul to Tue 21 Jul
OL,6,FSouthern areas are likely to start
OL,7,Fthis period very warm, locally hot in
OL,8,Fthe southwest, with heatwave
OL,9,Fconditions persisting. Somewhat cooler
OL,10,Fto the north and cloudy with periods
OL,11,Fof rain and drizzle in the far north.
OL,12,FInto the following week, high pressure
OL,13,Fis likely to build to the north or
OL,14,Fnorthwest of the UK, though its exact
OL,15,Forientation is rather more uncertain.
OL,16,FThis would bring a lot of dry weather
OL,17,Ffor many areas, though perhaps an
OL,18,Fincreased chance, relatively to
OL,19,Fprevious days, of showers or
OL,20,Fthunderstorms in the south.
OL,21,FTemperatures probably moderating a
OL,22,Flittle, though remaining above average
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Ffor many areas.
